oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The diorama of the Battle of Round Forest ("Hell's Half-Acre") located at the Museum and Visitors Center, Stones River National Battlefield, Murfreesboro, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The diorama pictures one of the unsuccessful attempts of the Southerners to drive the Federals from their position in Round Forest.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: J.T. Smith
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
